    <briefdescription>
<para>ASIO Compatibility Layer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Compatibility layer for websocketpp to work with newer standalone ASIO.</para>
<para>Problem:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>websocketpp expects <computeroutput>io_service</computeroutput> but newer ASIO (1.18+) uses <computeroutput>io_context</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>websocketpp hasn&apos;t been updated for ASIO 1.18+</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Solution:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Provides aliases and compatibility wrappers to bridge the gap</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Maps <computeroutput>io_service</computeroutput> -&gt; <computeroutput>io_context</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Maps deprecated APIs to modern equivalents</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This is a known compatibility issue in the websocketpp library </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
